title: Dan Neil (WSJ) & Aaron Robins (Car and Driver)
description: Dan Neil and Aaron Robinson stop by, they tell us about their time with the Pagani Huayra, and F12 Berlinetta, also we talk 911 Turbos, the Chinese car market, Pebble Beach, and the Dodge Dart.
author: matt@thesmokingtire.com (Matt Farah & Zack Klapman)
